LISAQHUBEKA nokubhebhetheka ngesivinini kuleli igciwane iCovid-19 njengoba izolo uMnyango wezeMpilo uveze ukuthi sesinyukele ku-45 973 isibalo sabantu osekuqinisekisiwe ukuthi bahaqwe yileli gciwane kuleli. UNgqongqoshe wezeMpilo uDkt Zweli Mkhize udalule lokhu ngoMgqibelo ebusuku lapho aveze khona ukuthi isibalo sabashonile sesiku-952 kuleli. Kwabashone kamuva, abawu-25 abaseWestern Cape, abayisithupha abaKwaZulu-Natal, abayisikhombisa abaseGauteng nabayisithupha base-Eastern Cape. UMkhize uthe noma sisakhuphuka isibalo sababulawe yileli gciwane, eNingizimu Afrika leli gciwane lisabulale kuphela u-2% wabantu abahaqekayo. Emhlabeni leli gciwane selibulale u-6% wabantu abathelelekile ngalo. IWestern Cape isahamba phambili ngesibalo sabantu abathelelekile njengoba bewu-30 379, okuwu-66% wabo bonke abantu abaphethwe yileli gciwane kuleli.  As of today, the cumulative number of confirmed COVID-19 cases is 45 973, the total number of deaths is 952 and the total recoveries is 24 258 pic.twitter.com/T62CJfeZzM #COVID19SouthAfrica Statistics as at 06 June 2020. pic.twitter.com/3RYyNl1Vz8 